ty — the brain's ability to reorganise itself by forming new neural connections — is the biological mechanism underpinning all learning, memory, and cognitive adaptation."}],"\n",["$","li","li-1",{"children":"AI personalisation of cognitive training leverages neuroplasticity principles to adapt difficulty, modality, and pacing to the learner's real-time neural feedback — outperforming fixed curricula."}],"\n",["$","li","li-2",{"children":"Consumer neurostimulation devices (tDCS, TMS) claim to enhance neuroplasticity — but the clinical evidence base for consumer applications remains limited and contested."}],"\n",["$","li","li-3",{"children":"The intersection of AI and neuroplasticity research is producing personalised therapeutic protocols for stroke rehabilitation, ADHD, and PTSD with early encouraging clinical results."}],"\n","$L25","\n"]}],"\n"]}],"\n## What If You Could Upgrade Your Brain Like You Upgrade Software?\n","$L26","\n","$L27","\n","$L28","\n","$L29","\n","$L2a","\n","$L2b","\n","$L2c","\n","$L2d","\n","$L2e","\n","$L2f","\n","$L30","\n","$L31","\n","$L32","\n","$L33","\n","$L34","\n","$L35","\n","$L36","\n","$L37","\n","$L38","\n","$L39"]
